<h3><a name="Bchapter_18" id="Bchapter_18"></a>EIGHTEEN</h3><div class="right"><A HREF="#Bchapter_17" class="nava" alt="Previous Chapter">&laquo;</A> <A HREF="#book_2" class="nava" alt="Table of Contents">&#94</A> <A HREF="#Bchapter_19" class="nava" alt="Next Chapter">&raquo;</A></div><div>

